<chapter version="2.0.0" number="8" name="Hills and Heights">
  <summary>
    The journey's final stretch through hill country with new territory guides. Terrain becomes challenging but beautiful. They reach the Ancient Grove and present Kira's question to Elder Heartwood - the ultimate plant authority who operates on month-long timescales. Now they wait for the response that will supposedly solve everything. Chapter ends with hope and anticipation, returning toward the settlement to await the answer.
  </summary>
  <focus>
    Building hope and anticipation. The majesty of Elder Heartwood and the Ancient Grove. Trust in ancient wisdom and authority. Deepening bonds between Kira and her plant companions during the journey. Setting up reader expectations for the coming disappointment.
  </focus>
